 <purpose>The Project application module supports the requirement to record programs of work for which one or more organizations are responsible, and relationships between projects. Events may be defined to specify when a project is planned to or actually starts and/or ends.
 </purpose>

 <inscope>
<li>establishing a data structure to identify programs of work;</li>
<li>establishing a data structure for relating the project to product data;</li>
<li>establishing a data structure for relating projects to one another;</li>
<li>indicating what organization or organizations are responsible for the project;</li>
<li>optionally representing a date or event when the project is planned to start;</li>
<li>optionally representing a date or event when the project is planned to complete;</li>
<li>optionally representing a date or event when the project actually started;</li>
<li>optionally representing a date or event when the project actually completed.</li>
 </inscope>

 <outscope>
<li>all concepts not involved in the specification of the concept of Project.</li>
 </outscope>

